"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt;\">	Add the PSG files containing the events to compare.<br />	For EDF files the .tsv file contains the events.</span></p>\n"
